Package: dockr
Title: Creation of Lightweight Docker Images for R Packages
Version: 0.8.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Lars",
           family = "Kjeldgaard",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "lars_kjeldgaard@hotmail.com")
Description: Build a lightweight Docker image from your R package, in which the
    package itself is installed and available. The image seeks to mirror your R 
    session as close as possible with respect to R specific dependencies.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
